Prager 20130905  2 Boots on the Ground?

Prager H2: Lee Habeeb fills in for Dennis and spends the hour discussing Syria, red lines,
 and whether or not we should put boots on the ground.

 He also shares one of his columns, Arab Like Me,

Prager 20130905  1 Just Keep Swimming

Prager H1: Lee Habeeb fills in for Dennis and talks with Bernie Marcus,
 co-founder and first CEO of Home Depot,
 about the state of small business in America.
 Small business owners weigh in to share their struggles.
